thread.title: Rosi
thread.title_full: White Mountain Puzzles reviewed by Rosi

author: Rosi
title: Rosi
text: I have only good things to say about White Mountain Puzzles ~ the puzzles are challenging and are of great quality. Customer service is top notch ~ they kept me informed of my order status every step of the way. Can't wait to finish one so I can start another so I can order more!
